page.title: 05CLUBS
page.content:
THE BROWNIES AT WELSH FRANKTON SIXES. The Brownies have different kinds of fairy folk names to represent each six. Here are each of the sixes and how many people are in each: Sprites 5, Pixies 5, Gnomes 5, Elves 2
RAMBLING BADGE. Thursday, June 6th. will be our last ramble for our badge. At a Brownies Rambler Meeting, we begin by giving in our 20p. admittance charge. We start our walk, which has to fit in between 6 and 7.30pm. Usually, we go down to the shop and Mrs. Horton and Mrs. Roberts buy us chewing gum and crisps and sometimes a bottle of pop to share with those who have no drink. Usually, we go across fields and stiles and streams and we see many different kinds of birds and flowers.
